{"tid":2460793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平行時空？H&M拒用新疆棉遭抵制 北京實體店仍爆滿","createTime":"2021-03-25T05:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:45:34.000Z","uid":13663,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ae01999c4dc189e2efe93ac583ddffac17cbd58c","tid":2460793,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"瑞典知名服裝品牌H&amp;M去年因「人權問題」，稱將不會採用來自新疆的產品或原材料，亦不會與當地任何服裝工廠合作。這條聲名昨晚（24日）被挖出，引爆中國從官媒、藝人到網友抵制聲浪，網路電商如淘寶、京東、拼多多等平台都火速下架H&amp;M所有產品，H&amp;M實體門市也一一在百度地圖上「被消失」。不過，H&amp;M實體店仍有絡繹不絕的顧客，店員一問三不知，抵制浪潮似乎只停留在網路。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據中國《中新經緯》報導，24日晚間7點30分許，北京市西單大悅城的H&amp;M門市仍有不少顧客選購，試衣間外也有很多顧客排隊。店員被問及是否清楚公司聲明抵制新疆產品一事時？店員只說：「不太清楚，我們有規定上班時間不讓帶手機。」另一名收銀員則稱剛來上班，不知道這件事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/fncnews/world/132405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffnc.ebc.net.tw%2Ffncnews%2Fworld%2F132405&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=f69e2759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/fncnews/world/132405</a>"},{"pid":"15b8186ff02a2adcc3c549a574519c1dfc0eb050","tid":2460793,"uid":13663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaAs96xtHJEbeyxivJcD7TeYJBh8JQzu7VjrKhv9wwGWd?filename=MDVVdL7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDVVdL7.gif&h=9bf4aff1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbf4cb137e7a1222a67f759330bd642d887d9bed","tid":2460793,"uid":118120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"就等同中國人手渣iphone講反美"},{"pid":"9553e57e855edb24b141668dfd77e33da2f8c192","tid":2460793,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"抵制日貨講咗一百年都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s